---
// Services.astro - Secci√≥n de servicios tipo mockup
---

<section id="services" class="w-full min-h-[70vh] bg-white flex items-center">
  <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-8 md:py-12">
    <h2 class="section-title">
      Our <span class="font-bold">Services</span>
    </h2>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16 mt-6">
      <!-- Columna izquierda: Imagen -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-[55%] xl:w-[60%]">
        <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-[16/9] relative">
          <img
            src="/services.png"
            alt="Services"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Columna derecha: Texto -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-[45%] xl:w-[40%] flex flex-col justify-center">
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light text-black mb-6 md:mb-8 text-left">
          Bring your vision to life through <span class="font-bold">web, mobile, and desktop solutions</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light text-black text-left">
          Crafted <span class="font-bold">fast</span> and <span class="font-bold">reliably</span>, by a <span class="font-bold">new generation of developers</span>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 